<body>
	
	<div class="top"></div>
		<section class="username">
			<div><%=email %></div>
			<a href="/auth/logout">Logout</a>
		</section>
		<div class="question">
			<p>What number, when written as a word, is the same whether it's written upside down or right side up? I was there when this game was started ðŸ˜†. </p>
